---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NavBar from '../../components/NavBar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy | ClaveON" description="Privacy Policy ClaveON" lang="en" canonicalPath="/en/datenschutz">
  <NavBar lang="en" />
  <main class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 680px;">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted);">
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-1" style="color: var(--text);">Controller</p>
          <p>José C. Martin Lache · Schirmerstr. 7 · 50823 Cologne, Germany · Email: info@claveon.de</p>
          <p style="margin-top:0.5rem;">No Data Protection Officer appointed under Art. 37 GDPR (sole trader, no systematic processing of special categories of data).</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-1" style="color: var(--text);">Data collected &amp; legal basis</p>
          <p>We only store data you voluntarily submit via the contact form (name, email address, optional phone number, message). The legal basis is Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR (pre-contractual measures) for handling your request.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-1" style="color: var(--text);">Contact form &amp; email delivery (data processor)</p>
          <p>Messages submitted via the contact form are transmitted through <strong>Brevo SAS</strong> (55 rue d'Amsterdam, 75008 Paris, France; <a href="https://www.brevo.com/legal/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--terra);">brevo.com/legal/privacypolicy</a>) as a data processor under Art. 28 GDPR. A Data Processing Agreement (DPA) is in place with Brevo. Data is not permanently stored on Brevo servers — it is used solely for email delivery.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-1" style="color: var(--text);">Hosting</p>
          <p>This website is hosted on <strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong> (Cloudflare, Inc., 101 Townsend St., San Francisco, CA 94107, USA). Technical access data (e.g. IP address, timestamp) may be temporarily processed. Cloudflare acts as a data processor under Art. 28 GDPR.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-1" style="color: var(--text);">Service Worker &amp; offline cache</p>
          <p>This website uses a Service Worker (sw.js) for PWA functionality. Static resources (CSS, fonts, images) are cached locally in your browser to allow the site to load under poor network conditions. No personal data is cached. The cache is automatically refreshed when the site is updated.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-1" style="color: var(--text);">Cookies &amp; tracking</p>
          <p>No tracking cookies. No analytics tools (no Google Analytics, no Matomo). No data sharing with third parties for advertising purposes.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-1" style="color: var(--text);">Your rights (Art. 15–21 GDPR)</p>
          <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.25rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; display: grid; gap: 0.3rem;">
            <li><strong>Access</strong> (Art. 15): Request a copy of the data we hold about you.</li>
            <li><strong>Rectification</strong> (Art. 16): Correct inaccurate data.</li>
            <li><strong>Erasure</strong> (Art. 17): Request deletion of your data.</li>
            <li><strong>Restriction</strong> (Art. 18): Restrict processing of your data.</li>
            <li><strong>Data portability</strong> (Art. 20): Receive your data in a machine-readable format.</li>
            <li><strong>Objection</strong> (Art. 21): Object to the processing of your data.</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">To exercise any of these rights, contact: <a href="mailto:info@claveon.de" style="color: var(--terra);">info@claveon.de</a></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-1" style="color: var(--text);">Right to lodge a complaint</p>
          <p>You have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority. The competent authority for this website is: <a href="https://www.ldi.nrw.de/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--terra);">State Commissioner for Data Protection and Freedom of Information NRW (LDI NRW)</a>, Kavalleriestraße 2–4, 40213 Düsseldorf, Germany.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-size: 0.85rem;">Last updated: March 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
